task.summary: Added syllable counting and file management.
Added words file and two example saved files to git.

Implemented 2 SQLite databases: - One based on google's list of 10,000 most common english words - One that contains tons of words with their syllable counts based on cmudict's pronunciation dictionary Replaced self-written time/date formatter with strftime Implemented file deletion Improved formatting of saved files Implemented high score tracking
